Enum SFMTParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SFMTParams>
      • com.github.okamumu.jmtrandom.SFMTParams
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SFMTParams>

    public enum SFMTParams
extends java.lang.Enum<SFMTParams>
    An enumerate class to provide the set of parameters for SFMT. For example, Params19937 represents the parameter set for SFMT with the period 2^19937-1.
